  "detailed_description": "《MechCrisis》It's a Roguelike shooter game<br><br>Warriors, hold on for 15 minutes! Resist the invasion of intelligent machinery<br><br>In a Roguelike extreme survival game, choosing different skills to level up makes each battle a new and exciting experience, with different characters having their own unique active skills, around which we can build our own gameplay each turn<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Refreshing shooting experience </h2>Have different weapons, experience different combat fun<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376870/extras/12735db306e55577b1de80cdff04ef26.poster.avif?t=1773210855\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376870/extras/12735db306e55577b1de80cdff04ef26.webm?t=1773210855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376870/extras/12735db306e55577b1de80cdff04ef26.mp4?t=1773210855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376870/extras/22b64a12c3a0e574c22fc8f02e72f6c4.poster.avif?t=1773210855\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376870/extras/22b64a12c3a0e574c22fc8f02e72f6c4.webm?t=1773210855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376870/extras/22b64a12c3a0e574c22fc8f02e72f6c4.mp4?t=1773210855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376870/extras/42ba0503949c5c7f7dd4c9a0f562e73e.poster.avif?t=1773210855\